Dear Sir/ Madam,






*I am mrs. Gift  Aba, the wife of late Engr Kwame Aba the former
biochemical head of  Anglo-gold Ashanti Ghana, who tested HIV positive and
died from Rock mining. I am also tested positive for AIDS virus and
pancreatic cancer, we have two children and based on the doctor's report. I
will soon die. Meanwhile, I am writing to seek your highly esteemed
help/consent in a lasting business relationship of mutual benefit involving
a treasure which my husband deposited with a security company for the
Adoption, up-keeping, and safe-keeping for my children as they will be
coming over to your country in due course to live and continue their school
since my days are numbered according to doctors report. Secondly after the
treasure is released to you it will be your responsibility to adopt and
take very good care of my kids since the treasure is worth taking care of
them and yourself for so many years.We should treat this confidentially for
some security reasons, please if you are ready to help my children and me,
please kindly indicate your interest so that I will tell you the next step
to take, I will be waiting for your Mail.Yours sincerely,Gift  Aba.*
